    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at Level 1 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for the declared model influence (Medium) and decision consequence (High) combination. The RHI < 1 regulatory criterion is satisfied at all five COU operating points with quantified output comparison bias within clinically acceptable bounds. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission claim that the test device does not exceed predicate device hemolysis under worst-case CPB operating conditions.",
